@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam usecaseFontSize 10

left to right direction

actor "Project Lead" as PL
actor "Team Member" as TM
actor "Viewer" as V

usecase "Xem danh sách\nsprint" as UC_List
usecase "Filter theo\nproject" as UC_Filter
usecase "Sort theo\nstatus" as UC_Sort
usecase "Xem chi tiết\nsprint" as UC_Detail
usecase "Expand/Collapse\nissue list" as UC_Expand

PL --> UC_List
TM --> UC_List
V --> UC_List

PL --> UC_Detail
TM --> UC_Detail
V --> UC_Detail

UC_Filter .up.> UC_List : <<include>>
UC_Sort .up.> UC_List : <<include>>

UC_Expand ..> UC_Detail : <<extend>>

note right of UC_Sort
  Sort order:
  1. ACTIVE (đầu)
  2. FUTURE
  3. CLOSED (cuối)
end note

note bottom of UC_Detail
  Hiển thị:
  • Sprint Name, Goal
  • Status badge
  • Start/End Date
  • Progress bar
  • Số issue hoàn thành/tổng
end note

@enduml
